name: Demiurgue, The creator | Metaverse series #001
description:
The artisan, the shaper of the world, the eternal creative, the computer of reality.

Beyond good and evil, dogmas and reality, beyond all that we can understand, Demiurge dwells.

After his last great reform to reality, he awakens in a world in chaos and entropy, ready for a new stage, a new world ...

The metaverse.
